{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-301-to-400/problem-302-strong-achilles-numbers","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"project-euler-problems-301-to-400","demoType":null,"title":"Vežba 302: Jačanje Ahilove tetive","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Pozitivan ceo broj $n$ je moćan ako je $p^2$ deljiv sa $n$ za svaki premijorni delilatelj $p$ u $n$.</p>\n<p>Pozitivan ceo broj $n$ je savršena potencija ako se $n$ može izraziti kao potencija drugog pozitivnog celog broja.</p>\n<p>Pozitivni savršeni broj $n$ je broj Ahileja ako je $n$ moćan ali nije savrstan stepen. Na primer, 864 i 1800 su brojevi Ahileja: $864 = 2^5 \\times 3^3$ i $1800 = 2^3 \\times 3^2 \\times 5^2$.</p>\n<p>Definisemo pozitivno savršeno broju $S$ moćan broj Akihilaja ako su i $S$ i $\\phi(S)$ brojevi Akihilaja. $\\phi$ označava funkciju totienta Eulera.</p>\n<p>Na primer, 864 je moćan broj Ahilaja: $φ(864) = 288 = 2^5 \\times 3^2$. Međutim, 1800 nije moćan broj Ahilaja jer: $φ(1800) = 480 = 2^5 \\times 3^1 \\times 5^1$.</p>\n<p>Postoje sedam snažnih Ahilova ispod ${10}^4$ i 656 ispod ${10}^8$.</p>\n<p>Koliko snažnih brojeva Ahilova je ispod ${10}^{18}?</p>\n</section>","id":"5900f49b1000cf542c50ffad","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"","notes":null,"challengeType":1,"helpCategory":"Euler","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"project-euler","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":301956,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-301-to-400/problem-302-strong-achilles-numbers"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"scriptjs","ext":"js","name":"script","contents":"function strongAchillesNumbers() {\n\n  return true;\n}\n\nstrongAchillesNumbers();","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["script.js"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p><code>strongAchillesNumbers()</code> treba da vrati <code>1170060</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(strongAchillesNumbers(), 1170060);"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/project-euler/#project-euler-problems-301-to-400","dashedName":"problem-302-strong-achilles-numbers","certification":"project-euler","disableLoopProtectTests":true,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"project-euler","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"project-euler-problems-301-to-400","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-301-to-400/problem-303-multiples-with-small-digits","prevChallengePath":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-301-to-400/problem-301-nim","id":"5900f49b1000cf542c50ffad","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":1,"challengeFiles":[{"name":"script","ext":"js","contents":"// solution required","history":["script.js"],"fileKey":"scriptjs"}]}},"id":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-301-to-400/problem-302-strong-achilles-numbers"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3858520367"],"slicesMap":{}}